items.name: ALLBITS
desc: All bits which are affected by this operation are set to 1.

items.name: INVERT
desc: All bits which are affected by this operation are inverted.

items.name: OVERPAINT
desc: sets all pixel as written in the output operation.

items.name: XOR
desc: uses the pixel written as one and the current pixel as the other operator of an exclusive or-operation.

items.name: ZEROBITS
desc: All bits which are affected by this operation are set to 0.
